# inGitDB Project Context

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for the complete AI agent guidelines.

## What This Repo Is

This is a **planning and architecture** repository for the inGitDB ecosystem — an open-source versioned database storing data in text files with Git-based version control.

It contains **documentation only**: Markdown files, an OpenAPI spec (YAML), and agent configs. No application source code.

## Key Documents

- `AGENTS.md` — Central AI agent guidelines (single source of truth)
- `development-plan.md` — Agent roles, prompts, 6-phase plan, tech stack, risks
- `openapi-spec.yaml` — Complete REST API specification (OpenAPI 3.0)
- `ingitdb-ts-architecture.md` — TypeScript client architecture
- `github-actions-integration.md` — CI/CD workflows and custom actions

## Constraints

- Do NOT create application source code (`.ts`, `.go`, `.js`) in this repo
- Do NOT modify `openapi-spec.yaml` unless explicitly instructed
- Reference existing docs rather than duplicating content
- Use relative links between documents
- Update `SUMMARY.md` when adding deliverables

## Tech Stack (for implementation repos)

- Server: Node.js/TypeScript or Go, JWT auth
- Client: TypeScript 5+, Rollup/tsup, Jest
- CLI: Go 1.21+, go-git
- CI/CD: GitHub Actions, Docker
